  "home.faq.title": "Frequently Asked Questions",
  "home.faq.q1": "What does GameTan actually measure?",
  "home.faq.a1": "GameTan measures 13 real gaming talent dimensions — reaction speed, pattern recognition, strategic thinking, multitasking, and more — through interactive mini-games. No personality quizzes. Your scores are compared against pro esports player benchmarks.",
  "home.faq.q2": "How accurate is the talent assessment?",
  "home.faq.a2": "Each mini-game is designed to isolate a specific cognitive or motor skill used in competitive gaming. Your results are ranked against data from professional esports athletes across FPS, MOBA, and strategy genres.",
  "home.faq.q3": "Is GameTan free to use?",
  "home.faq.a3": "Yes, the core talent test is 100% free. You get your full 13-dimension score breakdown, archetype classification, and pro comparison instantly after completing the 3-minute test.",
  "home.faq.q4": "What are the 16 gamer archetypes?",
  "home.faq.a4": "Based on your talent profile, you are matched to one of 16 gamer archetypes like Lightning Assassin, Oracle, Architect, or Berserker. Each archetype reflects a unique combination of strengths. Explore all archetypes to find yours.",
  "home.faq.q5": "Can I improve my scores?",
  "home.faq.a5": "Absolutely. GameTan identifies your strongest and weakest talent dimensions. Use the AI Coach to get personalized training advice based on your profile. Retake the test anytime to track improvement.",
